The defendant Toni M. Tolley was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Toni M. Tolley is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Toni M. Tolley was found guilty of Possess Drug Paraphernalia, an unclassified misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 961.573(1).
